1
00:00:08,220 --> 00:00:10,940
♪Hush now, don't disturb
the moonlight on the pond♪

2
00:00:11,940 --> 00:00:14,900
♪A shattered heart
rests pillowed in my chest♪

3
00:00:15,660 --> 00:00:17,580
♪I would shield you♪

4
00:00:17,580 --> 00:00:20,580
♪From this cruel wind and frost♪

5
00:00:22,980 --> 00:00:25,460
♪The russet cloth
brushes against my heart♪

6
00:00:26,420 --> 00:00:29,260
♪Like sunset
draping over your shoulders♪

7
00:00:30,020 --> 00:00:31,580
♪This lingering afterglow♪

8
00:00:31,580 --> 00:00:35,420
♪Holds the image
of our very first glance♪

9
00:00:36,460 --> 00:00:40,100
♪I borrow a thousand-year wind
to caress your gauze window♪

10
00:00:40,460 --> 00:00:44,420
♪Tailoring moonlight
into your luminous gown♪

11
00:00:44,900 --> 00:00:50,820
♪Severing the past,
weaving a thousand yards of splendor♪

12
00:00:51,380 --> 00:00:54,980
♪With a thousand-year dream,
I seek the fragrance of your hair♪

13
00:00:55,220 --> 00:00:58,700
♪Pouring a lifetime of passion
into the silk you wear♪

14
00:00:59,660 --> 00:01:05,660
♪In this splendid world,
wherever you are is paradise♪

15
00:01:05,980 --> 00:01:12,460
=The Silk Master from the Future=

16
00:01:12,580 --> 00:01:17,460
=Episode 8=
(This story is entirely fictional.)

17
00:01:18,280 --> 00:01:19,880
You're absolutely right, Li.

18
00:01:20,720 --> 00:01:22,080
Well, after some time,

19
00:01:22,080 --> 00:01:23,000
I'll find my sister

20
00:01:23,120 --> 00:01:24,680
a suitable husband

21
00:01:25,600 --> 00:01:26,320
and marry her off.

22
00:01:28,120 --> 00:01:29,120
That would be for the best.

23
00:01:29,880 --> 00:01:31,280
Now, let's get down to business.

24
00:01:31,920 --> 00:01:33,360
I can see that you two

25
00:01:33,360 --> 00:01:34,760
hail from the capital.

26
00:01:35,360 --> 00:01:37,320
And to have acquired the Xianquan Tavern

27
00:01:37,320 --> 00:01:38,600
in Feng City's bustling district,

28
00:01:38,960 --> 00:01:40,800
your family fortune
must be quite substantial.

29
00:01:42,160 --> 00:01:43,600
Thanks to the business
built by our ancestors,

30
00:01:43,920 --> 00:01:46,400
we do have a rather
comfortable family estate.

31
00:01:47,480 --> 00:01:48,880
Then, may I ask,

32
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:51,240
how substantial might that be?

33
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:55,520
If you'd rather not say, forget it.

34
00:01:56,160 --> 00:01:57,960
Let's cut to the chase
and speak plainly.

35
00:01:57,960 --> 00:02:00,040
I wish to invite you to join

36
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:02,680
the great grain price battle
in Feng City.

37
00:02:04,080 --> 00:02:06,920
Li Yunhe, so this "tremendous wealth"
you mentioned

38
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:09,200
means selling grain at inflated prices,

39
00:02:09,200 --> 00:02:10,200
profiteering from a national crisis,

40
00:02:10,200 --> 00:02:11,360
and earning blood money?

41
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:13,960
But as far as I know,

42
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:15,440
the Feng City government

43
00:02:15,440 --> 00:02:16,480
has no more silver

44
00:02:16,480 --> 00:02:17,600
to purchase grain.

45
00:02:17,880 --> 00:02:19,880
Who would you sell your grain to?

46
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:20,800
Exactly.

47
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:22,680
The refugees keep increasing,

48
00:02:22,720 --> 00:02:23,760
but the government has no money.

49
00:02:24,480 --> 00:02:26,880
Without funds, outside grain
cannot be brought into the game.

50
00:02:27,480 --> 00:02:28,800
Feng City's grain prices

51
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:30,480
will only climb higher and higher.

52
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:32,320
Entering the game at this point...

53
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:35,160
Forget making a profit,

54
00:02:35,320 --> 00:02:36,360
you'd be lucky

55
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:37,680
not to lose everything.

56
00:02:37,920 --> 00:02:39,040
Earlier today,

57
00:02:39,040 --> 00:02:41,080
I noticed your distinguished bearing

58
00:02:41,080 --> 00:02:42,200
and your extraordinary presence.

59
00:02:42,680 --> 00:02:44,520
You're certainly
no ordinary merchant's son.

60
00:02:44,880 --> 00:02:46,000
Now I see

61
00:02:46,080 --> 00:02:46,880
my judgment

62
00:02:46,880 --> 00:02:48,120
was indeed correct.

63
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:50,800
What do you mean by that, Li?

64
00:02:51,160 --> 00:02:52,920
The news
that the government treasury is empty

65
00:02:52,920 --> 00:02:54,200
isn't something an ordinary person

66
00:02:54,200 --> 00:02:55,280
could ever find out.

67
00:02:55,880 --> 00:02:56,560
Based on this alone,

68
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:57,720
I can conclude

69
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:58,680
that you must

70
00:02:58,680 --> 00:03:00,680
have a powerful background

71
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:01,960
and formidable strength.

72
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:03,960
You may not

73
00:03:04,160 --> 00:03:05,800
fully understand

74
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:07,480
what I'm about to say next,

75
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:08,480
but I'll

76
00:03:08,480 --> 00:03:09,880
explain it briefly.

77
00:03:37,200 --> 00:03:38,160
In short...

78
00:03:40,200 --> 00:03:41,560
What I intend to do next

79
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:43,080
is to buy long and sell short

80
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:44,360
and stabilize

81
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:46,800
Feng City's grain prices
in the shortest time possible.

82
00:03:46,880 --> 00:03:47,800
But rest assured,

83
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:49,680
every single coin we earn

84
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:51,600
will never come from the common people.

85
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:52,720
It will come from

86
00:03:52,720 --> 00:03:54,240
those unscrupulous merchants

87
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:55,960
who want to exploit the crisis
and earn blood money.

88
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:58,320
I've never heard of the method

89
00:03:58,320 --> 00:03:59,480
you speak of, Li.

90
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:01,080
But because you aim

91
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:01,880
to deal with those

92
00:04:01,880 --> 00:04:03,400
profiteers exploiting the crisis,

93
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:05,000
I'll trust you this once.

94
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:06,240
Alright, Zhuo.

95
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:08,760
To a pleasant partnership.

96
00:04:13,040 --> 00:04:14,080
To a pleasant partnership.

97
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:16,640
A pleasant partnership.

98
00:04:22,220 --> 00:04:26,260
(Zhou Manor)

99
00:04:32,080 --> 00:04:32,880
Yu?

100
00:04:35,240 --> 00:04:36,040
Li Yunhe?

101
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:44,840
Li Yunhe,

102
00:04:44,840 --> 00:04:46,480
where were you so late at night?

103
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:48,440
I went to meet with my friend.

104
00:04:49,160 --> 00:04:49,960
Don't worry,

105
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:52,160
I went to Xianquan Tavern,

106
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:53,080
not a brothel.

107
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:54,920
I didn't do anything to betray you.

108
00:04:55,440 --> 00:04:56,560
I wasn't suspecting you.

109
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:58,600
I was just asking.

110
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:03,160
The friend I met with this time,

111
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:04,760
you saw him at the Prefect's Office.

112
00:05:04,880 --> 00:05:06,000
His name is Zhao Yunzhuo.

113
00:05:06,200 --> 00:05:07,600
He's the owner of Xianquan Tavern.

114
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:10,280
With this grain price crisis

115
00:05:10,840 --> 00:05:12,080
and the Prefect's Office being broke,

116
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:14,240
I'm pulling him in
to act as the dealer with me

117
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:16,080
to tackle
this grain price crisis together.

118
00:05:16,200 --> 00:05:17,000
Act as the dealer?

119
00:05:17,960 --> 00:05:19,640
Wouldn't that take
an enormous amount of money?

120
00:05:19,760 --> 00:05:21,040
Do you need my help?

121
00:05:21,240 --> 00:05:22,680
I appreciate the offer,

122
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:23,680
but

123
00:05:23,680 --> 00:05:25,080
as a hired hand of the Zhou family,

124
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:26,640
where would you get that kind of money?

125
00:05:27,080 --> 00:05:27,600
I...

126
00:05:28,280 --> 00:05:29,120
Wait here a moment.

127
00:05:29,400 --> 00:05:30,640
I have a little surprise

128
00:05:30,640 --> 00:05:31,800
for you.

129
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:32,800
- A little surprise?
- Yeah.

130
00:05:33,840 --> 00:05:34,640
Wait here.

131
00:05:37,900 --> 00:05:40,750
♪Needle and thread stitch away♪
(Zhou Manor)

132
00:05:40,750 --> 00:05:43,860
♪The marks of time♪

133
00:05:43,860 --> 00:05:47,540
♪Cutting a yard of the misty rain♪

134
00:05:47,540 --> 00:05:50,540
♪Embroidering half a scroll
of earthly verses♪

135
00:05:50,540 --> 00:05:53,100
♪Where the golden honors hang high♪

136
00:05:53,100 --> 00:05:57,180
♪The clouds dance in the air♪

137
00:05:57,180 --> 00:06:00,420
♪Brewing wine, we speak of legends♪

138
00:06:00,420 --> 00:06:04,060
♪In fine liquor,
true feelings are revealed♪

139
00:06:04,380 --> 00:06:07,260
♪In this life I'd be a cloud-tailor♪

140
00:06:07,260 --> 00:06:13,900
♪Never failing the stars,
nor failing you♪

141
00:06:14,860 --> 00:06:19,340
♪A single bolt of silk becomes♪

142
00:06:20,180 --> 00:06:24,900
♪Your wedding gown♪

143
00:06:29,400 --> 00:06:30,880
Zhou Xingyu! Have you gone mad?

144
00:06:32,440 --> 00:06:33,040
You're using fifty percent

145
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,720
of the Zhous' ready silver
to speculate on grain?

146
00:06:34,720 --> 00:06:35,720
Fifty percent!

147
00:06:35,840 --> 00:06:37,480
Aren't you worried
you might lose everything?

148
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:39,440
I trust Li Yunhe.

149
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:42,200
Li Yunhe is nothing
but a live-in son-in-law.

150
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:43,200
You'd gamble the entire Zhous' fortune

151
00:06:43,200 --> 00:06:44,600
just for his sake?

152
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:45,360
Like I said,

153
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:47,600
I trust Li Yunhe.

154
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:49,280
Even if you trust him,

155
00:06:49,280 --> 00:06:50,920
and you make money this time,

156
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:53,000
for Li Yunhe's sake,

157
00:06:53,200 --> 00:06:54,840
you'll make the Zhou household

158
00:06:54,840 --> 00:06:56,080
the enemy the Marquis House.

159
00:06:56,080 --> 00:06:57,040
Do you realize that?

160
00:06:57,200 --> 00:06:58,360
Is doing this

161
00:06:58,360 --> 00:06:59,880
really worth it?

162
00:07:00,440 --> 00:07:01,240
Have you forgotten?

163
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:02,520
The reason I chose a live-in husband

164
00:07:02,520 --> 00:07:04,120
in the first place was to avoid

165
00:07:04,200 --> 00:07:05,240
the forced marriage
from the Marquis House.

166
00:07:05,440 --> 00:07:07,000
Since he joined my family,

167
00:07:07,400 --> 00:07:08,800
I must protect him.

168
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:10,400
Besides,

169
00:07:11,400 --> 00:07:12,440
the official decree
revoking our family's

170
00:07:12,440 --> 00:07:13,440
imperial supplier status

171
00:07:13,440 --> 00:07:14,440
has not yet arrived.

172
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:15,200
If the Marquis House

173
00:07:15,200 --> 00:07:17,000
wants to move against us now,

174
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:18,200
they'll have to weigh carefully

175
00:07:18,200 --> 00:07:20,000
how His Majesty
would view such a matter.

176
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:21,280
Fine.

177
00:07:21,280 --> 00:07:23,000
I can't out-argue you.

178
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:24,240
You have your reasons.

179
00:07:28,220 --> 00:07:29,500
(Proclamation)

180
00:07:30,520 --> 00:07:31,440
Government proclamation.

181
00:07:31,440 --> 00:07:33,320
(Proclamation)
Due to the necessity of disaster relief,

182
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:35,680
this office intends to purchase grain
in large quantities

183
00:07:35,680 --> 00:07:37,000
to replenish the government granaries.

184
00:07:37,200 --> 00:07:38,400
To widely attract grain sources,

185
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:39,640
we hereby offer to purchase

186
00:07:39,640 --> 00:07:41,360
(Grain price: 180 coins per hodful)
at a price higher than the market rate.

187
00:07:41,440 --> 00:07:43,080
(Grain Price: 220 coins per hodful)
220 coins per hodful.

188
00:07:43,320 --> 00:07:45,400
(Xinfeng Grain Shop)
Grain price is 220 coins per hodful.

189
00:07:45,400 --> 00:07:48,000
- 220 coins?
- That's outrageous!

190
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:49,680
- Way too expensive!
- Truly outrageous!

191
00:07:49,880 --> 00:07:51,400
220 coins per hodful?

192
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:52,280
It's all that worthless

193
00:07:52,280 --> 00:07:53,320
Li Yunhe's idea!

194
00:07:53,680 --> 00:07:55,600
Yeah! It's Li Yunhe's fault!
Let's get him!

195
00:07:55,960 --> 00:07:57,840
(Zhou Manor)
Li Yunhe, you scumbag!

196
00:07:58,120 --> 00:08:00,000
- Get out here, Li Yunhe!
- Come out if you dare!

197
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:01,000
- Get out here!
- Get out!

198
00:08:02,200 --> 00:08:03,000
Hey!

199
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:04,680
Folks,

200
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:06,280
what's the grain price situation now?

201
00:08:06,760 --> 00:08:07,160
Get him!

202
00:08:07,320 --> 00:08:07,680
Get him!

203
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:08,360
Attack!

204
00:08:08,360 --> 00:08:09,120
Let's get him!

205
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:09,560
Get him!

206
00:08:11,400 --> 00:08:13,360
Everyone!

207
00:08:15,120 --> 00:08:15,720
Calm down.

208
00:08:16,280 --> 00:08:17,440
Let's talk nicely.

209
00:08:17,440 --> 00:08:18,680
Don't waste food.

210
00:08:18,800 --> 00:08:21,000
Li Yunhe,
you're such a rotten scoundrel.

211
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:21,800
You colluded with the government,

212
00:08:21,800 --> 00:08:22,800
driving up grain prices.

213
00:08:22,840 --> 00:08:23,240
It's already

214
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:24,800
220 coins per hodful now!

215
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:26,080
220 coins?

216
00:08:26,800 --> 00:08:27,200
This rate

217
00:08:27,400 --> 00:08:29,400
of increase isn't good enough.

218
00:08:29,400 --> 00:08:31,200
- Not good enough?
- You want it to keep going up?

219
00:08:31,200 --> 00:08:31,960
Alright,

220
00:08:31,960 --> 00:08:33,000
keep cursing then.

221
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:33,800
Get down here!

222
00:08:33,800 --> 00:08:34,680
Come down!

223
00:08:35,400 --> 00:08:36,280
Get down here!

224
00:08:37,040 --> 00:08:38,160
Get down here now!

225
00:08:38,920 --> 00:08:39,680
Come down!

226
00:08:39,980 --> 00:08:42,380
(Grain Price: 220 coins per hodful)

227
00:08:42,660 --> 00:08:45,220
(Grain Price: 260 coins per hodful)

228
00:08:45,400 --> 00:08:47,500
Today's grain price
is 260 coins per hodful.

229
00:08:47,520 --> 00:08:50,880
- It went up again?
- Way too expensive!

230
00:08:50,880 --> 00:08:52,000
Why is this grain so expensive?

231
00:08:52,800 --> 00:08:53,600
It's all that worthless

232
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:55,000
Li Yunhe's rotten idea!

233
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:56,000
Let's go confront him!

234
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:56,840
- Let's go.
- Yeah.

235
00:08:58,840 --> 00:09:00,080
- Get down!
- Get down here!

236
00:09:01,400 --> 00:09:02,480
Come down!

237
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:04,200
Get out here!

238
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:05,240
Come out now!

239
00:09:06,200 --> 00:09:07,280
Wait!

240
00:09:08,800 --> 00:09:10,400
What's the grain price now?

241
00:09:10,400 --> 00:09:11,800
You conscienceless scumbag!

242
00:09:11,800 --> 00:09:13,240
It's 260 coins now!

243
00:09:13,240 --> 00:09:14,400
Where's your conscience?

244
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:16,280
260 coins?

245
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:17,800
Not bad.

246
00:09:17,800 --> 00:09:19,240
Now that's what I call a proper surge.

247
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:21,000
- Attack him!
- Let's attack him!

248
00:09:21,560 --> 00:09:23,000
But it's almost peaked, you know.

249
00:09:23,840 --> 00:09:24,280
Peaked?

250
00:09:24,280 --> 00:09:25,200
Why not make it 300 then?

251
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:27,480
Still not enough for you at 260?

252
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:28,440
- Stop wasting food.
- Get down!

253
00:09:28,440 --> 00:09:30,080
My family can't even
finish all our vegetables.

254
00:09:30,080 --> 00:09:31,040
Is anyone thirsty?

255
00:09:31,240 --> 00:09:32,800
How about I treat you all to some tea?

256
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:34,840
This is insufferable.

257
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:35,640
We can't endure this!

258
00:09:36,560 --> 00:09:37,040
Hey!

259
00:09:38,040 --> 00:09:38,560
Tea?

260
00:09:40,700 --> 00:09:43,600
(Marquis House)

261
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:44,920
(Marquis House)
What's the grain price now?

262
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:46,520
Feng City's grain price

263
00:09:46,520 --> 00:09:48,400
has gone completely insane.

264
00:09:48,440 --> 00:09:49,520
In just two days,

265
00:09:49,520 --> 00:09:50,400
it's already shot up

266
00:09:50,400 --> 00:09:52,000
to 280 coins per hodful.

267
00:09:52,040 --> 00:09:53,280
We're making a fortune!

268
00:09:54,800 --> 00:09:55,840
Have them

269
00:09:55,960 --> 00:09:57,400
sell all the grain

270
00:09:57,400 --> 00:09:59,120
to me.

271
00:09:59,400 --> 00:10:00,880
But didn't we just

272
00:10:00,880 --> 00:10:02,520
offload a batch?

273
00:10:02,520 --> 00:10:03,440
What a fool.

274
00:10:04,680 --> 00:10:06,320
Don't you see
the government is still raising prices?

275
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:07,800
With the government as a safety net,

276
00:10:07,960 --> 00:10:09,400
prices can keep climbing.

277
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:10,280
Mobilize

278
00:10:10,280 --> 00:10:12,000
all forces
around the Marquis House's domain.

279
00:10:12,320 --> 00:10:14,400
Have them sell all their grain to me.

280
00:10:14,880 --> 00:10:16,160
But grain prices outside the city

281
00:10:16,160 --> 00:10:17,400
have also gone mad.

282
00:10:17,400 --> 00:10:18,600
And besides, does the government

283
00:10:18,600 --> 00:10:20,000
even have money left to buy grain?

284
00:10:20,400 --> 00:10:21,480
Relax.

285
00:10:22,120 --> 00:10:24,320
The government must provide
disaster relief in the end.

286
00:10:24,320 --> 00:10:25,800
Buy it all

287
00:10:25,800 --> 00:10:28,600
as long as the price
is lower than Feng City's.

288
00:10:29,920 --> 00:10:32,120
My lord, there's word

289
00:10:32,120 --> 00:10:34,080
that the Zhous have also jumped in.

290
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:36,800
Can we afford that much?

291
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:40,400
They think they can compete
with me in wealth in Feng City?

292
00:10:40,640 --> 00:10:41,800
They're delusional.

293
00:10:42,040 --> 00:10:43,040
Buy as much as there is

294
00:10:43,040 --> 00:10:44,640
in the market.

295
00:10:44,640 --> 00:10:46,200
When civil unrest erupts,

296
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:48,000
people will tear the Zhous apart.

297
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:51,400
Then, I will take the opportunity
to pacify the unrest,

298
00:10:51,400 --> 00:10:52,600
seize the Zhou family assets,

299
00:10:52,680 --> 00:10:54,600
and make another massive profit.

300
00:10:55,040 --> 00:10:57,320
Might this offend
the natural order of heaven?

301
00:10:58,440 --> 00:10:59,800
Sir, to be honest,

302
00:10:59,880 --> 00:11:00,720
recently, the steward

303
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:01,960
disbursed a very large sum of money.

304
00:11:02,400 --> 00:11:03,160
What?

305
00:11:03,160 --> 00:11:05,040
My family is also hoarding grain?

306
00:11:05,720 --> 00:11:07,120
Don't worry, Xie.

307
00:11:07,280 --> 00:11:08,760
This matter of making money

308
00:11:08,840 --> 00:11:09,880
is a tremendous good thing

309
00:11:09,880 --> 00:11:11,280
for your family.

310
00:11:11,640 --> 00:11:13,080
Zichen, go.

311
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:14,400
Take Mr. Xie with you

312
00:11:14,400 --> 00:11:16,160
and earn big money together.

313
00:11:17,040 --> 00:11:18,440
Truly brilliant, my lord.

314
00:11:18,440 --> 00:11:19,480
I'll see to it right away.

315
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:20,280
Haha.

316
00:11:20,960 --> 00:11:23,360
Come, Xie, this way.

317
00:11:35,400 --> 00:11:37,080
Madness. This is sheer madness!

318
00:11:37,880 --> 00:11:38,760
A hodful of rice in Feng City

319
00:11:38,760 --> 00:11:39,720
has now reached

320
00:11:39,720 --> 00:11:40,960
290 coins.

321
00:11:41,200 --> 00:11:42,360
If this keeps up,

322
00:11:42,400 --> 00:11:43,760
forget the common folk,

323
00:11:43,760 --> 00:11:44,560
even I

324
00:11:44,560 --> 00:11:46,360
find it unaffordable, Yunzhuo.

325
00:11:46,800 --> 00:11:48,080
What does Li Yunhe say?

326
00:11:49,360 --> 00:11:50,400
Buy to fill the warehouses.

327
00:11:50,400 --> 00:11:51,360
Continue the water route shipments.

328
00:11:51,360 --> 00:11:52,480
Transport grain to Feng City.

329
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:54,720
When will the court's

330
00:11:54,720 --> 00:11:55,560
disaster relief grain arrive?

331
00:11:56,080 --> 00:11:56,960
Your Majesty,

332
00:11:56,960 --> 00:11:58,880
it should be another few days or so.

333
00:11:59,240 --> 00:12:00,400
Any movement

334
00:12:00,400 --> 00:12:01,560
over at the Zhou Manor?

335
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:03,400
Their actions

336
00:12:03,400 --> 00:12:04,640
are almost synchronized with ours.

337
00:12:04,840 --> 00:12:06,040
How far along are they?

338
00:12:06,160 --> 00:12:07,480
By a rough estimate,

339
00:12:07,480 --> 00:12:09,280
the silver the Zhous
have thrown into this

340
00:12:09,280 --> 00:12:11,480
accounts for seventy percent
of their liquid funds.

341
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:12,560
It seems

342
00:12:12,560 --> 00:12:13,320
that I have

343
00:12:13,320 --> 00:12:14,680
underestimated that live-in son-in-law's

344
00:12:14,680 --> 00:12:16,080
standing in the Zhou family.

345
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:18,160
Send word down.

346
00:12:18,560 --> 00:12:20,120
Do as Li Yunhe says.

347
00:12:20,400 --> 00:12:21,640
Yes, Your Majesty.

348
00:12:21,640 --> 00:12:25,420
(Grain Price: 290 coins per hodful)
Grain price is 290 coins per hodful.

349
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:27,160
Buy it all.

350
00:12:28,560 --> 00:12:29,360
Ship it.

351
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:31,460
(Xinfeng Grain Shop)
Grain price is 300 coins per hodful.

352
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:33,080
Buy it all.

353
00:12:33,080 --> 00:12:33,920
Ship it.

354
00:12:34,520 --> 00:12:35,160
My lord,

355
00:12:35,160 --> 00:12:36,720
another shipment of grain has arrived.

356
00:12:36,720 --> 00:12:37,480
It came by water. Shall we take it...

357
00:12:37,480 --> 00:12:37,960
Take it.

358
00:12:37,960 --> 00:12:38,920
Take it all!

359
00:12:38,960 --> 00:12:40,360
I'm taking as much as they ship.

360
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:41,520
The government is our safety net anyway.

361
00:12:41,520 --> 00:12:41,960
Do it.

362
00:12:41,960 --> 00:12:42,720
Understood.

363
00:12:53,620 --> 00:12:55,920
(Xinfeng Grain Shop)

364
00:12:55,920 --> 00:12:57,120
(Xinfeng Grain Shop)
We're from Pengshan Prefecture,

365
00:12:57,120 --> 00:12:58,040
here to sell grain.

366
00:12:58,040 --> 00:12:58,680
Unload the grain.

367
00:12:58,680 --> 00:12:59,320
Unload.

368
00:13:05,320 --> 00:13:07,240
Your Majesty, the Marquis House

369
00:13:07,240 --> 00:13:08,720
has once again bought up all the grain

370
00:13:08,720 --> 00:13:10,120
we transported.

371
00:13:11,040 --> 00:13:12,200
Insatiably greedy.

372
00:13:14,720 --> 00:13:16,120
Continue shipping grain to Feng City.

373
00:13:17,040 --> 00:13:19,040
I'd like to see just how much

374
00:13:20,280 --> 00:13:22,280
the Marquis House can swallow.

375
00:13:22,520 --> 00:13:23,200
Buy it.

376
00:13:23,400 --> 00:13:24,400
Ship it.

377
00:13:25,240 --> 00:13:25,960
Buy it.

378
00:13:26,120 --> 00:13:27,320
Ship it.

379
00:13:28,320 --> 00:13:28,960
Buy it.

380
00:13:29,120 --> 00:13:29,720
Ship it.

381
00:13:30,160 --> 00:13:32,120
Buy it all!

382
00:13:32,320 --> 00:13:33,720
Keep shipping it.

383
00:13:34,780 --> 00:13:36,820
(Zhou Manor)
Get the hell out!

384
00:13:36,820 --> 00:13:39,300
- Come out right now!
- Get out here!

385
00:13:39,320 --> 00:13:40,920
Chunxiang, tell the steward

386
00:13:40,920 --> 00:13:42,600
to continue distributing grain
to the people at the gate.

387
00:13:42,720 --> 00:13:43,560
My lady,

388
00:13:43,560 --> 00:13:45,520
the Zhou family's grain
is nearly depleted.

389
00:13:45,520 --> 00:13:46,640
But more and more people

390
00:13:46,640 --> 00:13:47,520
are coming to curse.

391
00:13:47,520 --> 00:13:48,520
There are even new faces.

392
00:13:48,520 --> 00:13:49,920
If this continues,

393
00:13:49,920 --> 00:13:50,680
the situation

394
00:13:50,680 --> 00:13:52,000
might spiral out of control.

395
00:13:52,440 --> 00:13:53,440
What...

396
00:13:59,520 --> 00:14:00,240
Huaijin.

397
00:14:00,240 --> 00:14:02,160
What are you looking at me for?

398
00:14:02,800 --> 00:14:04,000
I'm not going to help him.

399
00:14:05,520 --> 00:14:05,920
Huaijin,

400
00:14:06,200 --> 00:14:07,520
send your family's grain

401
00:14:07,520 --> 00:14:08,480
over here.

402
00:14:08,960 --> 00:14:10,120
Just consider that I owe you.

403
00:14:10,280 --> 00:14:10,840
I'll definitely

404
00:14:10,840 --> 00:14:12,560
repay you double later. Is that alright?

405
00:14:12,720 --> 00:14:14,560
Xingyu, you know full well

406
00:14:14,560 --> 00:14:16,720
the grain price outside has skyrocketed.

407
00:14:16,960 --> 00:14:17,960
The Marquis House is already

408
00:14:17,960 --> 00:14:20,000
hoarding grain in massive quantities.

409
00:14:20,280 --> 00:14:22,160
You want to keep
wading deeper into this?

410
00:14:22,360 --> 00:14:24,280
Are you determined
to follow this path to its dark end?

411
00:14:24,880 --> 00:14:25,720
Besides,

412
00:14:25,720 --> 00:14:27,120
you're working yourself to the bone,

413
00:14:27,280 --> 00:14:28,400
and what's Li Yunhe doing?

414
00:14:28,720 --> 00:14:30,800
He's leisurely sipping tea.

415
00:14:31,360 --> 00:14:32,960
Tell me,
what are you even doing this for?

416
00:14:33,080 --> 00:14:34,400
Li Yunhe has already given
more than enough

417
00:14:34,400 --> 00:14:35,680
for the Zhou family.

418
00:14:35,880 --> 00:14:36,680
Besides,

419
00:14:36,680 --> 00:14:38,400
if he really loses this time,

420
00:14:38,760 --> 00:14:39,680
the Marquis House

421
00:14:39,680 --> 00:14:41,280
won't spare us.

422
00:14:41,520 --> 00:14:42,680
If you'd just divorced him earlier,

423
00:14:42,680 --> 00:14:43,960
we wouldn't be in this mess today.

424
00:14:44,280 --> 00:14:46,120
In Feng Cheng's tiny patch of land,

425
00:14:46,160 --> 00:14:48,600
who can fight against the Marquis House?

426
00:14:49,280 --> 00:14:51,680
Just accept your fate, Xingyu.

427
00:14:52,480 --> 00:14:54,080
I don't believe
fate is something you just accept.

428
00:14:54,480 --> 00:14:56,520
It's something you fight to earn.

429
00:14:58,400 --> 00:14:59,200
Fine.

430
00:14:59,680 --> 00:15:00,960
Since you've put it that way,

431
00:15:02,080 --> 00:15:03,720
I'll send word to my family

432
00:15:04,080 --> 00:15:05,240
to send grain and money.

433
00:15:05,560 --> 00:15:06,680
But if by noon tomorrow,

434
00:15:06,680 --> 00:15:08,520
people are still gathered at the gate,

435
00:15:08,720 --> 00:15:10,080
for the Zhou household's safety,

436
00:15:10,120 --> 00:15:11,760
he must go out and face them himself.

437
00:15:12,480 --> 00:15:13,600
Alright.

438
00:15:13,600 --> 00:15:14,680
I knew

439
00:15:14,680 --> 00:15:15,880
you'd definitely help me.

440
00:15:16,280 --> 00:15:17,080
Humph.

441
00:15:18,700 --> 00:15:21,220
(Grain Price: 330 coins per hodful)

442
00:15:21,960 --> 00:15:22,560
Today's grain price:

443
00:15:22,560 --> 00:15:24,320
330 coins per hodful.

444
00:15:24,880 --> 00:15:25,880
(Xinfeng Grain Shop)
330 coins per hodful?

445
00:15:26,120 --> 00:15:27,280
(Xinfeng Grain Shop)
Grain price is this high now?

446
00:15:27,400 --> 00:15:29,800
- Li Yunhe should drop dead!
- Drop dead!

447
00:15:29,880 --> 00:15:30,880
- He should go to hell!
- Yeah!

448
00:15:31,520 --> 00:15:33,720
Right now, the public fury
outside the walls is sky-high.

449
00:15:33,720 --> 00:15:35,200
You're truly not the least bit worried?

450
00:15:35,320 --> 00:15:36,600
If you're still a man,

451
00:15:36,920 --> 00:15:38,280
you'll march your way out there.

452
00:15:39,480 --> 00:15:40,280
Oh, right.

453
00:15:40,520 --> 00:15:42,120
Help me pass a message
to the government office, will you?

454
